high_descs: Look down and turn to the left.
Pick up the coffee cup on the table.
Turn left and take one step, then turn to the right and take three steps, then turn to the left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the cup inside, close the door for three seconds, then take the cup out of the fridge.
Turn around and take one step, then turn left and walk across the room.
Place the coffee cup on the shelf to the left of the book.
Turn to the left and face the counter
Grab the mug off of the counter
Head straight and go to the fridge
Put the mug on the top rack in the fridge and then close the door. Then take out the mug
Turn right and go to the brown shelves
Put the mug on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: Putting a cooled mug on a shelf

high_descs: Turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the mug that's in front of you.
Turn left and walk past the counter on your right then turn right and walk to the fridge and turn left when you get to it to face it.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the shelves on the far wall and stop about three feet short of it and take a small step to your right.
Put the mug to the left of the book on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the shelf.
